{"product_id":"nurme-neroli-delicate-cleansing-micellar-water-200ml","title":"NURME Neroli Delicate Cleansing Micellar Water 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eThis gentle micellar water, enriched with hyaluronic acid and pro-vitamin B5, thoroughly removes makeup while soothing the skin. A blend of neroli and passion fruit extracts leaves a smooth, even complexion, suitable for all skin types.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eNeroli oil, derived from bitter orange blossoms, has powerful antimicrobial and antibacterial properties, ideal for acne-prone skin and clogged pores. It helps regulate sebum production and balance oily skin. Rich in antioxidants and vitamin E, neroli oil has anti-aging and anti-acne benefits, combating free radicals and reducing inflammation and redness.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003eSoak a cotton pad or cloth and gently wipe over eyes and face.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Citrus Aurantium Dulcis Flower Water*, Glycerin**, Citrus Aurantium Amara Flower Water*, Panthenol*, Sodium Benzoate**, Cocamidopropyl Betaine**, Potassium Sorbate**, Lactic Acid**, Benzyl Alcohol**, Sodium Hyaluronate**, Passiflora Incarnata Extract*.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* Natural origin\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e** Natural cosmetics approved ingredient\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"Nurme","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50915901604167,"sku":null,"price":12.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/nurme-neroli-delicate-cleansing-micellar-water-200ml-991849.jpg?v=1739897173","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/nurme-neroli-delicate-cleansing-micellar-water-200ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}